## Overview

In this project, we perform an end-to-end customer churn analysis—exploring key churn drivers and building predictive models to forecast customer churn. The goal is to empower businesses to anticipate churn risk and take proactive retention measures.

---

## Dataset

The dataset used is `WA_Fn-UseC_-Telco-Customer-Churn.csv`, containing features such as demographics, account information, and customer usage patterns. :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}

---

## Project Structure

Churn Analysis - EDA.ipynb # Exploratory Data Analysis
├── Churn Analysis - Model Building.ipynb # Feature engineering & ML modeling
├── Customer Churn Knowledge.py # Reusable scripts & helper functions
├── WA_Fn-UseC_-Telco-Customer-Churn.csv # Raw data
├── model.sav # Serialized trained model
├── tel_churn.csv # Processed dataset
